{"tid":208843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港千萬富翁調查2016 學生竟然佔千萬富翁的2%","createTime":"2017-04-19T19:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T09:03:56.000Z","uid":104513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5d6c85481e63ba914edc6f1d2598b022ba4d3e","tid":208843,"uid":104513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:52:33.000Z","msg":"花旗銀行「香港千萬富翁調查2016」顯示，以21歲至79歲港人計算，2016年全香港有87.8萬名擁有百萬元以上流動資產的百萬富翁，按年升14%，創下歷史新高。至於千萬富翁，全港有5.9萬名，但按年並無增長。<br />\n<br />\n至於幾高人工先能夠踏上千萬富翁的階梯？統計指出，千萬富翁打工仔的月入中位數為17.5萬元！屬就業市場月入中位數的11倍。<br />\n<br />\n當中47%千萬富翁為打工仔，只有高級管理層、僱主同專業人士，其他冇份。非打工仔佔53%，退休人士佔整體四成，學生竟然佔千萬富翁的2%（約1,250名）！而主婦都有8.5%（約5,000名）左右。<br />\n<br />\n千萬富翁的流動資產中位數為2,000萬元，究竟佢哋持有乜嘢資產？有36%為現金（2015年為45%），27%為股票（2015年為30%），互惠基金及債券共佔三成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b9395c0890d7b75a966d2609695e1956540def","tid":208843,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:53:52.000Z","msg":"有咩事都有錢過世"},{"pid":"db4840a0c4e4fce9133174e5b78e89d6f2ed1d92","tid":208843,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩事都有錢過世</blockquote><br />\n未計樓都過千萬 點黎⋯⋯"},{"pid":"afb5569ca1945d44ba0f0e3d6271d863c9f6b153","tid":208843,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩事都有錢過世</blockquote><br />\n未計樓都過千萬 點黎⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n現金 啲富豪比仔扎下袋咋"},{"pid":"e15c7ca3d953b9d61bc0d45b9ec1cc5be87e2b82","tid":208843,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩事都有錢過世</blockquote><br />\n未計樓都過千萬 點黎⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n現金 啲富豪比仔扎下袋咋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbf575ab455986166cb234de37872b769a7b495","tid":208843,"uid":96658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:26:37.000Z","msg":"因為有錢到唔洗打工<br />\n重返校園做學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6999993193d25730852ce3a55f2f04e0ff711316","tid":208843,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T21:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩事都有錢過世</blockquote><br />\n未計樓都過千萬 點黎⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n零用錢黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6016614078e95c0fc9ce7c977a355acf308f6674","tid":208843,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T21:13:54.000Z","msg":"係美國睇一次醫生都幾十萬到過百萬<br />\n冇返咁多錢點做有錢人呀"},{"pid":"0c47dc8cfef2ea66be8150d0cbf0d92892b7c104","tid":208843,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩事都有錢過世</blockquote><br />\n未計樓都過千萬 點黎⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n零用錢黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8284fd46068dabd972cd9cbd4ce8127e8edd8301","tid":208843,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:59:44.000Z","msg":"原來都有千幾個同我一樣"},{"pid":"465c561394042fc95f79421ec65d7bc179627020","tid":208843,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來都有千幾個同我一樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包養我"}]}